{"tid":1608552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請立刻籌備記者會，宣布香港進入戰爭狀態。","createTime":"2019-10-01T10:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T11:30:28.000Z","uid":22047,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"57898f56f84750308b65d9e901cb68b3bbb2c5b0","tid":1608552,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"我地冇大台，冇人做到代表講宣言。<br />\n而泛民係呢次運動入面做唔到代表既角色；反而最多人睇，外面既人認為最有公信力既，就係民間記者會。<br />\n我懇求民記，慎重考慮預備一篇宣言，成個記者會淨係圍繞呢篇宣言為主題。<br />\n第一，向外宣佈香港已進入戰爭狀態；<br />\n第二，向國際求援<br />\n我個人認為唔需要刻意提到獨立，如果請到人道求援，自然可以達到真正自治。<br />\n呢篇宣言，係前線義士用條命同你換返黎。請好好使用今日既材料，否則，香港人只會習慣真槍實彈同無辜既死亡。<br />\n民記，呢鋪真係靠哂你地。"},{"pid":"2ff28d63fee8deaaa53b3c62fe14a5203fc584cc","tid":1608552,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:47:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f92e6a05d42ddf60c6a46381acfdf42440d7493","tid":1608552,"uid":174541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港人治港 剷除共黨</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">正名!</span></span><br />\n狗 --&gt; 港共走狗/共狗打手/金腰帶<br />\n示威者 --&gt; 香港人<br />\n死--&gt;被自殺<br />\n藍絲--&gt;港共流氓<br />\n<br />\n光頭警長劉Sir前往内地安家，民眾甚感期待<br />\n光頭<span style=\"color: red;\">走狗</span>劉Sir前往内地安家，民眾甚感期待<br />\n<br />\n[底已起] 又有隻奶共狗話示威者係曱甴<br />\n[底已起] 又有隻奶共狗話<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人</span>係曱甴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權! 撐政府一律捆綁式形容!</span></span>"},{"pid":"f7c18a919118e91c6c5760a33375990397bbae9c","tid":1608552,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:49:20.000Z","msg":"正確方向"},{"pid":"1d952c7d579f228147f86ea0999d2a7dcf10179d","tid":1608552,"uid":286735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:49:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7e7716321c34713c6463b8e15224ea81eeb9e20","tid":1608552,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4f2e550124c9d094551abcb125cad3c9e8695ac","tid":1608552,"uid":22047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"行動上必須激進少少，其中包括：<br />\n1. 呼籲各國撤僑；<br />\n2. 歡迎反共國家既軍醫及軍隊進駐香港。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充。"},{"pid":"39265ee1ffd80f536bcfec9e5bc43a39d358d934","tid":1608552,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"黑警沖入人群開槍 <br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/ksnrt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fksnrt&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=7582f8aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/ksnrt</a><br />\n<br />\n另一近角度<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/9g1f6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F9g1f6&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=15707bb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/9g1f6</a>"},{"pid":"28dfa4de9888643476d2ba64d76433bb636e94eb","tid":1608552,"uid":315090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e5960c495e75b9d3946a99fa7c00163aeab7524","tid":1608552,"uid":80200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:55:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2a579623f86488ccae4ab160f5ba7a590c59d2a","tid":1608552,"uid":246741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:55:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dcd8493ccdf1170ffca7f0564f2def8dd46be7a","tid":1608552,"uid":137171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1608455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1608455/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"95d0d5f1d0b1549d8affac30704eea499c4229be","tid":1608552,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"但我亦必須提醒大家，民記並唔係唯一希望。咁多次記者會佢地既立場唔係最偏激，民記大部分都係敘述事實既一個平台，好少會作出宣言。<br />\n<br />\n所以若果民記唔做，我地只可成立一個宣言團隊出黎，另謀出路。"},{"pid":"12725921efff4a5a1008eebb792ad8bdae3ba677","tid":1608552,"uid":157865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"c9cd98fbbe888eaff8b8d2b7cde78801ee411ff6","tid":1608552,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"要求聯合國駐軍"},{"pid":"2f0a68b60913ffa26389911be090050a44ee0473","tid":1608552,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dcd8493ccdf1170ffca7f0564f2def8dd46be7a","tid":1608552,"uid":137171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1608455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1608455/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:57:45.000Z","msg":"就咁係連登講係冇用，我當你有十萬人上連登，仲有幾百萬人睇唔到。記者會唔同，記者會幫你向外reach到全部讀者，人數一定遠超連登。"},{"pid":"2df67969082c15c50ef397699abb5fc565043a45","tid":1608552,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4f2e550124c9d094551abcb125cad3c9e8695ac","tid":1608552,"uid":22047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"行動上必須激進少少，其中包括：<br />\n1. 呼籲各國撤僑；<br />\n2. 歡迎反共國家既軍醫及軍隊進駐香港。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscWZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=fc40ac95\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-polic